filter.description:
Add a Jira filter to monitor. You can find the Filter ID in the URL when viewing a saved filter in Jira.

If you don't provide a filter name, the system will automatically use the name from Jira.

{test_result}

add_filter.description:
Add a new Jira filter to monitor.

If you don't provide a filter name, the system will automatically use the name from Jira.

{test_result}

edit_filter_details.description:
Update the filter information.

If you don't provide a filter name, the system will automatically use the name from Jira.

{test_result}
